edu.mtu.cs3421.voto.VotoComponents

Class MessageUtility

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.mtu.cs3421.voto.VotoComponents.MessageUtility

  • public class MessageUtility
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Nicholas Schweikart on 3/1/17. This provides a static set of utilities to parse incoming and outgoing Voto messages.
